{"tid":1786720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我喺華為office見到啲好有趣嘅野 (2)","createTime":"2019-12-17T10:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T15:16:02.000Z","uid":226739,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"bc9fd6490fca07456d244e3e40bbd851fb70ce68","tid":1786720,"uid":226739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:45:27.000Z","msg":"原post：我喺華為office見到啲好有趣嘅野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786496</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>是咁的，早幾個月有日因為要做野而入咗華為office，一入門口就見到啲好有趣嘅野：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19Y5dC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19Y5dC7.jpg&h=ab7fb0b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（為免俾華為或我公司起我底，所以我只能油黑啲登記資料）<br />\n<br />\n请无香港工作签的同事领取访客证<br />\n请无香港工作签的同事领取访客证<br />\n请无香港工作签的同事领取访客证<br />\n<br />\n無工作簽證嘅員工，咁即係話&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係又簽紙扮訪客 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後成間office周圍都貼住「訪客區」，啲「訪客」個個對住電腦「做自己嘢」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnfvpKB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnfvpKB.jpg&h=e9709656&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zgu8bpC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzgu8bpC.jpg&h=b2858f2b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ch5bTCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCh5bTCZ.jpg&h=2ba2f7d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我將呢啲資料俾咗入境處，但等咗幾個月都淨係得 auto reply，唔通扮訪客呢招真係 work？<br />\n入境處唔做野，咁唯有公開俾大家啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 登記時見到都有啲係填HKT，似乎係真訪客，咁即係話HKT都知華為有呢種「訪客員工」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6731f31d5ed7978268c6cbf868e54c65c05a04d8","tid":1786720,"uid":226739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"原post 爆咗"},{"pid":"0ab73635012f75005c4b6c0ff749c259bde9d948","tid":1786720,"uid":205109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bbed0482b302ec6705e19bfcc4ce0ebf2c720517","tid":1786720,"uid":8532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"入境事務處24小時電話系統舉報熱線（電話：(852)2824 1551）<br />\n或電郵至anti_crime@immd.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncomplaints@ombudsman.hk<br />\n申訴專員公署 投訴email<br />\n<br />\n1823<br />\ntellme@1823.gov.hk"},{"pid":"60e7cae1b59aa2a4e008fe5c4d022a80f2486592","tid":1786720,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce95b88dcc7837039649d01312fac255511008a5","tid":1786720,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:51:48.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"0e594855ff75aeceed3910d0d50488a3eb313bb4","tid":1786720,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc9fd6490fca07456d244e3e40bbd851fb70ce68","tid":1786720,"uid":226739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T10:45:27.000Z","msg":"原post：我喺華為office見到啲好有趣嘅野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786496</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>是咁的，早幾個月有日因為要做野而入咗華為office，一入門口就見到啲好有趣嘅野：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/19Y5dC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F19Y5dC7.jpg&h=ab7fb0b2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n（為免俾華為或我公司起我底，所以我只能油黑啲登記資料）<br />\n<br />\n请无香港工作签的同事领取访客证<br />\n请无香港工作签的同事领取访客证<br />\n请无香港工作签的同事领取访客证<br />\n<br />\n無工作簽證嘅員工，