"2019-12-17T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e727c9d101fb1f6b6714fdd6a1c03acd1f9c82","tid":1786720,"uid":238863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:24:10.000Z","msg":"有朋友現職係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時係會有入境去巡既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但每次都會收到風話一陣有人黎<br />\n會即刻叫啲大陸佬/冇工作簽既人即刻散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個office就會無左大半人<br />\n<br />\n咁點解會收到風 同埋 係邊到收到風 <br />\n我就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e8cf3aac21fe3a54f23e8e873c266125fe0192","tid":1786720,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"同過佢哋香港員工傾計，話有唔少人係呢啲用一週一行落嚟做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n入境處點會做嘢，係做就唔到今時今日都未聽過有人被拉。"},{"pid":"64f89746d3774b587de31de05f77694953e09f04","tid":1786720,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93e727c9d101fb1f6b6714fdd6a1c03acd1f9c82","tid":1786720,"uid":238863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:24:10.000Z","msg":"有朋友現職係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時係會有入境去巡既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但每次都會收到風話一陣有人黎<br />\n會即刻叫啲大陸佬/冇工作簽既人即刻散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個office就會無左大半人<br />\n<br />\n咁點解會收到風 同埋 係邊到收到風 <br />\n我就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"真係有一半黑工，支国大單位，點會准你拉。"},{"pid":"7e5b9a462cb1ba1308188e9183084bddd6eb63cd","tid":1786720,"uid":49908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcqZ4bU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcqZ4bU.png&h=8e087029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">乜嘢叫多眼位，好明顯係大陸人寫嘅句子連當眼位都唔識以為自己已學好香港話廣東話</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"d9524902faec4781ca0f1204b683ccaf49dbda7b","tid":1786720,"uid":269481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"咁撚大間野都做到咁低裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea80270f9cc0ebd583b890c96ca15f120268baa","tid":1786720,"uid":8566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"已投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd1e89407001057d1baff6ea56bfb4697629392","tid":1786720,"uid":169690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"推 黑工喎，入境處去咗邊"},{"pid":"de4bea69707a8c2351410f029adab4e372dd9089","tid":1786720,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]